{"tid":866031,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"老馬親自向美斯解釋言論遭曲解","createTime":"2018-10-17T14:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T03:21:13.000Z","uid":20634,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"104cae85b663e3a97bba0fee6cb607a556396a5d","tid":866031,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/1/381/23250612381/23264665251_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F1%2F381%2F23250612381%2F23264665251_600x399.jpg&h=60de7d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n較早前有報道指馬勒當拿呼籲美斯別重返國家隊，並多次批評後輩在國家隊的演出，可能又是世紀誤會。<br />\n<br />\n「馬勒當拿的意思是，阿根廷不該單靠美斯（Lionel Messi），而非說美斯不是領袖。」31歲的美斯在世界盃後仍未重返國家隊，老馬的律師莫拿周一晚表示：「巴塞隆拿都是踢整體足球，每個人都表現良好。」<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥電視台較早前報道，57歲的馬勒當拿馬狂插美斯，不僅叫該巴塞巨星別再重返國家隊，又爆對手在國際賽前往往要去洗手間20次。<br />\n<br />\n「老馬批評美斯的言論不是真確，關於洗手間的說法是被記者引導，實情非如此，老馬之後會打電話給美斯，解釋他的說法，當中無意向他施壓，事實正好相反。」莫拿重申受訪時是為美斯辯護，絕非火上加油，故此將會親自致電給美斯解釋言論，但不會作出道歉。<br />\n<br />\n「美斯在國際賽前是比較緊張，但老馬想說不是他的錯，有錯是全隊共同承擔。」莫拿補充道。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"00656c5fe5969ac7a756e8b307a792f619ac6ad6","tid":866031,"uid":3454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T15:01:45.000Z","msg":"老馬驚佢有牙咩<br />\n1&gt;0😂"},{"pid":"2b8f307342cb2ad69a634796aad02736666585a8","tid":866031,"uid":44285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00656c5fe5969ac7a756e8b307a792f619ac6ad6","tid":866031,"uid":3454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T15:01:45.000Z","msg":"老馬驚佢有牙咩<br />\n1&gt;0😂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"😂😂"},{"pid":"3a30e3dd2e88ae5b171bf6c02e551f2bf224f755","tid":866031,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T02:25:18.000Z","msg":"球霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老馬講下真心話都要解釋道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1136213ffec51f26cdf4f632dd3e1d339b78f765","tid":866031,"uid":141543,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T02:45:52.000Z","msg":"老馬都知得罪尾球王冇好下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6242bb35a754b8fb98490a7c80b56ecedf8edc68","tid":866031,"uid":33709,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:21:13.000Z","msg":"成個阿根廷都係靠佢 得罪佢真係變三流球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}